# 🔵 5. When to Use Index?
👉 Use index on columns used in:

- ✔ WHERE
- ✔ JOIN
- ✔ ORDER BY
- ✔ GROUP BY

Example:
SELECT * FROM orders
WHERE customer_id = 10;
👉 Add index on customer_id

..........................................................
..........................................................

# 🔴 6. When NOT to Use Index? (Very Important)

- ❌ Small tables (no benefit)
- ❌ Columns with many duplicates (low cardinality)
- ❌ Frequently updated columns

# 👉 Why?
   Index slows down INSERT/UPDATE

