# ⚡ 7. Composite Index Rule (Golden Rule)
👉 Leftmost Prefix Rule
Index:- 
(department, salary)

Works:- 
WHERE department = 'IT'
WHERE department = 'IT' AND salary > 50000

❌ Doesn't Work:
WHERE salary > 50000
👉 Because department is first column

